dh-virtualenv (1.1-1) UNRELEASED; urgency=medium

  * New: Add --extras option (#243) [@jhermann]
  * Maint: Python 3.4 and 3.5 added to test environments (#238) [@jhermann]
  * Fix: Support new style shebangs generated by recent pip (#226) [@nailor]
  * Fix: New build dependendcies (dh-exec + python-sphinx-rtd-theme) (#231) [@labeneator]
  * Fix: Disallow building a package whilst within an activated virtualenv (#224) [@lamby]
  * Fix: Use 'python -m pip' instead of direct pip calls (#219) [@moritz]
  * Fix: Ignore --extra-pip-arg in call for --upgrade-pip (#197) [@jhermann]
  * buildsystem: Allow to specify a virtualenv name (#180) [@dzen]
  * docs: Improved structure, new chapters [@jhermann]
  * docs: Fix reference to pbuilder's USENETWORK option (#246) [@mkohler]

